      "insufficiency:text": "The behavioral-programs.md source material contains a full reference section on useBehavioral (useBehavioral factory pattern, publicEvents filtering, context injection, async initialization, manual lifecycle management) which is not represented in the behavioral-seed. The seed focuses on core bThread/bSync primitives and agent-specific patterns but does not include useBehavioral as a named anchor.",
