      "insufficiency:section": "Reusable Behavioral Programs with useBehavioral",
      "insufficiency:impact": "medium — useBehavioral is a valid BP factory pattern in this codebase; downstream factory generation should know about it",
      "insufficiency:proposedAnchor": "behavioral:useBehavioral-factory",
      "insufficiency:justification": "behavioral-seed did not include useBehavioral because it is not used in the agent-loop integration surfaces currently. However, behavioral-programs.md contains detailed documentation of this pattern, making it part of the corpus evidence surface.",
